  "time_ut": 1657732426,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bb4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Tripartite's request for permission to launch a counter attack was rejected",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The party leaders have rejected the request made by the commanders of the three forces and the Inspector General of Police to give permission to carry out a counter attack in case of an attack on the Parliament by the protestors.",
        "If Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe steps down as Acting President, an initial resolution to the current unrest could be reached. The party leaders have insisted that if he resigns, the speaker can be appointed as the acting president and look into the next steps.",
        "A special party leader's meeting was held on 13th Wednesday at the parliament building under the chairmanship of Speaker Mahindayappa.",
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe have been demanding the resignation of Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "People's struggle has intensified after Ranil Wickremesinghe was sworn in as the acting president. Communist Party Acting President Weerasinghe Weerasumana has insisted that Ranil Wickramasinghe should step down from the post of acting president considering the safety of the people of the country.",
        "The Chief Whip of the opposition party, Laxman Kiriella said that in the party leader's meeting, the commanders of the three forces mentioned that they urged the president to resign considering the current critical situation in the country.",
        "The party leaders have refused the request made by the commanders of the three forces and the police chief to give permission to carry out a counter attack to control the situation if the protestors attack with the aim of besieging the Parliament.",
        "It was pointed out in the party leader's meeting that the security forces should not cooperate with the decisions taken by the government against the constitution.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe did not participate in the party leader's meeting. The only solution to the current situation is for President Ranil Wickremesinghe to step down, Laxman Kiriella said.",
        "After the resignation of Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe, an idea was put forward in the party leader's meeting to appoint the Speaker as the Acting President and take a look at the next steps."
      ],
